byline.contributor: Ellen Barry reported from New Delhi, and Salman Masood from Islamabad, Pakistan. Hari Kumar contributed reporting from New Delhi, and Sameer Yasir from Srinagar, Kashmir.
byline.original: By ELLEN BARRY and SALMAN MASOOD

lead_paragraph: Pakistan played down the early morning operation, which it said killed two of its soldiers and wounded nine, calling it a propaganda exercise by Delhi.
